      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single quasi-static loading rate (5 mm/min) in ambient laboratory conditions only. No elevated-temperature or physiological-fluid environment testing was conducted. Only one ASTM F1717 configuration (compression-bending) was evaluated; torsion and tension configurations were out of scope for this COU. Achieved level 2 falls below the required level 3 for this factor at Model Risk 3. This shortfall is acknowledged; the gap is partially offset by the close agreement between the two independent laboratories, but the single-condition limitation remains unresolved."
