    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is noted and judged acceptable given the strong inter-laboratory agreement (CV < 3%) and the pre-established acceptance criteria being met for all three QoIs across all 11 specimens. The overall body of evidence is judged sufficient to support a Medium assurance conclusion for the non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending COU.",
